name: InspireMe
0:
”Alexa, open inspire me and tell me something inspiring”
”start inspire me”
”repeat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspire me
des:
Wanted to feel inspired and motivated? Alexa got you covered. 
Enable "Inspire Me" skill and Invoke by saying "inspire me" or "tell me something inspiring".

This skill serves the user with motivational and inspirational quotes and sayings from the greatest minds.
Stay Motivated! Stay Inspired!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
